      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks! this is a great start. can u dive a bit deeper into section 3 and 6? like, if i'm writing about how to look and act \"sophisticated\" and \"professional\" on a global level, what are the baseline standards i should tell my readers to follow? give me some specific examples of what that looks like for dress and dining so they have a solid foundation.",
